  {\sf pop\_list: intlist\rightarrow intlist\times int }\  \text{for}\  {\sf pop}
  \end{array}
~
the linker will compute a different "future" for the program i.e.  
~Math
 \begin {array}{l}
{\sf pop (push\ 2 \ empty)} \&  \\
  {\sf pop\_list*(Cons*\ 2 * [\ ])}
\end{array}
~

